('ardfin', 'Ardfin', '', '', 'No', 'No', '', '', '', 'islands', '', 55.800457, -6.013064, 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 0, 'b', 0xe61000000101000000100533a6600d18c0596dfe5f75e64b40, 'nonlinks', 'Yes', 'Ardfin Golf Course, located on the Isle of Islay, is a private and exclusive course set amidst breathtaking coastal scenery. The layout weaves through rolling hills, woodlands, and dramatic sea cliffs, offering golfers a strategic challenge and a visually stunning experience. Its undulating fairways and carefully positioned bunkers reward accuracy and thoughtful approach shots, while the greens are contoured to test putting skills.  The course\'s design integrates the natural landscape, allowing the surrounding vistas, including ocean views and rugged Islay terrain, to enhance each hole. Strategic hazards and elevation changes demand careful club selection and tactical planning, making it a true test of skill.  Ardfin Golf Course is recognized for its exclusivity, high-quality maintenance, and exceptional natural beauty. Every round is immersive, blending challenge, tranquility, and scenic pleasure. The combination of dramatic coastal scenery, strategic design, and a peaceful environment ensures that golfers experience a memorable and rewarding Scottish golfing adventure.', ''),
