('loudoungowf', 'Loudoun Gowf', 'https://loudoungowf.hub.clubv1.com/Visitors/TeeSheet', 'https://loudoungowf.hub.clubv1.com/Visitors/TeeSheet', 'Yes', 'Yes', 'clubv1', 'clubv1', '', 'glasgow', 'Yes', 55.605190, -4.363000, 0, 0, '', '', 'loudoungowf', 132, '', 0, 0, 'e', 0xe61000000101000000c1caa145b67311c0e1eeacdd76cd4b40, 'nonlinks', 'No', '', ''),
('Luffness', 'Luffness New', 'https://www.luffnessnew.com/visitor-booking/', 'https://www.luffnessnew.com/visitor-booking/', 'No', 'No', '', '', 'mon,tue,wed,thu,fri,sun', 'eastlothian', '', 56.022171, -2.842449, 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 'b', 0xe610000001010000001b62bce655bd06c0b6f5d37fd6024c40, 'links', 'No', 'Luffness New Golf Club is a titan of East Lothian golf and one of the most traditional clubs in the world. Founded in 1894, the course was designed by Old Tom Morris, and it remains a pure, unadulterated links experience. Luffness is famous for its lack of modern \"clutter\"-there are no yardage markers, no flashy signage, and a strict adherence to traditional dress codes and etiquette. It has a formidable tournament pedigree, having served as a Final Qualifying venue for the Open Championship for decades.\r\n\r\nThe course is a sanctuary of fast-running turf, deep revetted bunkers, and thick, punishing rough. Notable members have included legends of the game and members of the British establishment who value its privacy and tranquility. Unlike the hilly Gullane nearby, Luffness is relatively flat, but the wind is a constant and brutal defender of par. The clubhouse is a time capsule of 19th-century golfing elegance, and the lunch is as famous as the greens. To play Luffness is to step back into the \"Golden Age\" of golf, offering a quiet, serious, and immensely rewarding links challenge.', '');
