('trumpold', 'Trump International - Old', 'https://www.trumpgolfscotland.com/', '', 'Yes', 'No', 'trumpAberdeen', '', '', 'aberdeen', 'Yes', 57.277429, -2.020530, 14851, 0, '', '', '', 0, '', 0, 1, 'a', 0xe61000000101000000eeb1f4a10b2a00c022fb20cb82a34c40, 'links', 'Yes', 'Located at Balmedie in Aberdeenshire, Trump International is one of the most talked-about modern courses in the world. Designed by Dr. Martin Hawtree and opened in 2012, it is a massive, spectacular links built amidst some of the tallest sand dunes in Europe. The course is a \"modern-traditional\" masterpiece where every hole is secluded from the others by towering ridges of marram grass. It has quickly become a mainstay for elite events and is often cited for its \"Tour-standard\" conditioning.\r\n\r\nThe course is notorious for its difficulty, especially when the North Sea wind channels through the valleys. Notable for its 14th hole, which offers a panoramic view of the coastline, and its \"Great Dunes\" it is a visual and physical test of the highest order. The club features a luxurious, five-star clubhouse and a world-class practice facility. While it is a relatively new addition to the Scottish landscape, it has already established itself as a world-ranking titan that demands every shot in a golfer\'s bag.', ''),
